HEADWORD: Theoretical
<hw>The`o*ret"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/: cf. L.
<ets>theoreticus</ets>, F. <ets>th⟦eacute⟧or⟦eacute⟧tique</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Pertaining to theory; depending on, or confined to, theory or
speculation; speculative; terminating in theory or speculation: not
practical; <as>as, <ex>theoretical</ex> learning; <ex>theoretic</ex>
sciences.</as></def> -- <wordforms><wf>The`o*ret"ic*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
